{"tid":886802,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[妳們的女神]雞排妹戀上日版孔劉 男友狂影私密照","createTime":"2018-11-02T11:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T01:09:28.000Z","uid":12558,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8aae81784f748dee8d6569d7e1d77ae87b118118","tid":886802,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:31:21.000Z","msg":"台灣藝人「雞排妹」鄭家純身材火辣，一向都唔吝嗇身材，係好多宅男心目中嘅女神，不過早前雞排妹被指做咗第三者，同導演李伯恩兩度密會，報道一出，雞排妹即刻喺ig澄清冇咁嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n點解咁急否認呢？可能係唔想男友擔心啦，係呀，雞排妹真係拍拖了！最近有台灣傳媒報道，雞排妹同一位貌似孔劉嘅日本兒科醫生拍拖，雞排妹仲讚男友耐心又溫柔，仲幫佢影咗唔少相。<br />\n<br />\n其實雞排妹啱啱開始學日文，今年初去咗日本生活3個月，當時受訪時已經講過，用交友app認識咗呢位日版孔劉，不過當時佢話驚咗long D，只係當對方朋友。不過最近雞排妹致力向日本發展，又帶隊開日本團陪玩陪食陪拍照，多咗時間喺日本，同日版孔劉拍拖都係理所當然嘅事喇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TqNyxMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqNyxMw.png&h=410dec6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9OBvyd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9OBvyd.png&h=e3f53921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i33Rjrz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi33Rjrz.png&h=d67e3fed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CdPEtjV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCdPEtjV.png&h=e573e51c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2606e511b16384fe08ab66284340599d5fb5231c","tid":886802,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"真係鄭家純<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f759eae5744dd995098e7133ec5054fccf05c51","tid":886802,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:43:57.000Z","msg":"AV孔劉 - 森林原人"},{"pid":"a446759c41e6552427f0c13c2a5deb5667d88870","tid":886802,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"咩app識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.